stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending
    Pending --> PartiallyFulfilled: First valid allocation
    Pending --> Fulfilled: Full allocation in one run
    PartiallyFulfilled --> PartiallyFulfilled: Additional partial allocations
    PartiallyFulfilled --> Fulfilled: Remaining volume reaches zero
    Pending --> Cancelled: Manual cancellation
    PartiallyFulfilled --> Cancelled: Manual cancellation
    Fulfilled --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
